Comm (Commune)
=================
comm <message>   - Send a message to all fellow priests in the game.
comm -tail       - Print last 20 messages said on the channel.
comm -toggle     - Turn your channel on or off.
comm -mass       - Is there a mass going on?
 
Without argument shows the priests in game.
 
You can also use 'channel priest send' instead of 'comm'.
